Vietnam 's Communist Party Chief to Visit Laos
HANOI , February 27 ( Xinhua ) -- Vietnam 's Communist Party chief Le Kha Phieu is to pay an official visit to Laos in the near future , it was announced here Friday .
This will be the first trip abroad by Phieu since he became the General Secretary of the Communist Party at the end of last December .
The visit is in response to an invitation from the President of the Laos People 's Revolutionary Party Khamtay Siphandone who was elected President of the Laos People 's Democratic Republic this week .
Sources here said the visit is arranged to show the solidarity and special relationship between the two parties and two neighboring countries .
